{"tid":385169,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"港男老公唔喺身邊　人妻白雲同馬仔纏綿","createTime":"2017-09-03T04:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T23:44:49.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b2c793dbffe393a96d53a8595603cca1d084a38c","tid":385169,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T04:00:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170902/large/1504327252_d52e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170902%2Flarge%2F1504327252_d52e.jpg&h=458e4f37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白雲<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170902/large/1504327263_1ae0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170902%2Flarge%2F1504327263_1ae0.jpg&h=569a3520&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170902/large/1504327272_ddfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170902%2Flarge%2F1504327272_ddfe.jpg&h=dd887696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170902/large/1504327282_b30f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170902%2Flarge%2F1504327282_b30f.jpg&h=b7a6aa0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170902/large/1504327293_8ad7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170902%2Flarge%2F1504327293_8ad7.jpg&h=66fda209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170902/large/1504327302_e167.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170902%2Flarge%2F1504327302_e167.jpg&h=fa5c20bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170902/large/1504327445_235c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170902%2Flarge%2F1504327445_235c.jpg&h=b8137f85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170902/large/1504327462_a51d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170902%2Flarge%2F1504327462_a51d.jpg&h=9f652e07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳浩康(左)和雄霸馬主鍾國良<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170902/large/1504327492_4958.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170902%2Flarge%2F1504327492_4958.jpg&h=8541bc9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莫家淦(左)、陳國峰(左二)、張振朗(右)、吳業坤(右二)<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170902/large/1504327528_0525.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170902%2Flarge%2F1504327528_0525.jpg&h=1c5cd1ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n潘頓與麥菲文 (右)<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170902/large/1504327547_966c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170902%2Flarge%2F1504327547_966c.jpg&h=9d3161e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麥菲文副練余詠詩 (左)<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170902/large/1504327645_4647.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170902%2Flarge%2F1504327645_4647.jpg&h=d81e266c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n右起：潘頓、祈普敦、貝湯美、麥菲文、史卓豐、柏寶、郭能<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170902/large/1504327688_ebfc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170902%2Flarge%2F1504327688_ebfc.jpg&h=31c06725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙田馬場這天有甚多藝人出沒，原來新在港開倉的澳洲籍練馬師麥菲文，在馬房內舉行季前拜神儀式，「雄霸」馬主鍾國良拉大隊邀請不少藝人好友出席撐場，非常畀面，包括張振朗、陳國峰、吳業坤、莫家淦、白雲及吳浩康等，十分熱鬧。<br />\n<br />\n其中去年已下嫁前港男江俊霖嘅35E人妻，曾飾演節目《五覺大戰》「神獸天使」嘅白雲，唔知係咪太索關係，連馬房內嘅馬仔都俾佢吸引到，白雲去到一匹四班馬「善影」嘅馬格前面，同「善影」一齊玩自拍嘅時候，這匹馬忽然好似遇見女神咁，猛咁挨住白雲，好溫柔咁用個鼻摸摸白雲香肩及頸，兼且嗅吓佢嘅香水味，白雲則喺度傻笑，同「善影」纏綿合照，玩得好開心。<br />\n<br />\n此外，五班馬「友歡笑」亦非常搞笑，在馬房內經常點頭，像跟訪客打招呼般，近期在劇集《踩過界》飾演傷殘人士偵探，人氣急升的張振朗，都忍唔住為該駒拍片。<br />\n<br />\n至於騎師方面，今朝有潘頓、貝湯美、郭能、柏寶、史卓豐、祈普敦出席拜神儀式。麥菲文說：「這是我第一次參加中國傳統的拜神儀式，就算我過往在新加坡練馬時都未試過切燒豬、上香。副練余詠詩教我拜神程序，感覺新鮮。我馬房有許多質新馬，希望牠們盡快適應水土建功，我新季的目標是獲得25場頭馬或以上。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/racing/20170902/57160054\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fracing%2F20170902%2F57160054&d=HRfJxQQ%2BkWe4jdeiczQ95uargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=a7451641\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fracing%2F20170902%2F57160054&h=c3d681b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/racing/20170902/57160054</a>"},{"pid":"39c9e0d713ef12f62513757aba99a2cbfa0bea91","tid":385169,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T04:42:04.000Z","msg":"負評上一頁"},{"pid":"d1ee9b0e55c9f6c80a82dedfa1fdf177441f13a8","tid":385169,"uid":52571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:33:22.000Z","msg":"睇錯馬雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1815bf46a7793e894f1e97cfb782eb2fab8a66fb","tid":385169,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T23:44:49.000Z","msg":"<strong>阮兒救一命　白雲35E導彈差啲破衫而出</strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170903/photo/bkn-20170903083626996-0903_00862_001_01b.jpg?20170903091232\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170903%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170903083626996-0903_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20170903091232&h=f4b546cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影張相都好易有意外！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170903/photo/bkn-20170903083626996-0903_00862_001_02b.jpg?20170903091232\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170903%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170903083626996-0903_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20170903091232&h=acabefe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原本合照都冇乜嘢，大家都好靚女～<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170903/photo/bkn-20170903083626996-0903_00862_001_03b.jpg?20170903091232\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170903%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170903083626996-0903_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20170903091232&h=2d8e8ac4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇路呀白雲（右）。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170903/photo/bkn-20170903083626996-0903_00862_001_04b.jpg?20170903091232\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170903%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170903083626996-0903_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20170903091232&h=1c96bdb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一跣就跣足兩級。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170903/photo/bkn-20170903083626996-0903_00862_001_05b.jpg?20170903091232\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170903%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170903083626996-0903_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20170903091232&h=9db3d894&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好在有阮兒（左一）喺旁邊扶實咋！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170903/photo/bkn-20170903083626996-0903_00862_001_06b.jpg?20170903091232\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170903%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170903083626996-0903_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20170903091232&h=c5ad71bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好在35E冇出嚟「見人」&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170903/photo/bkn-20170903083626996-0903_00862_001_07b.jpg?20170903091232\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170903%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170903083626996-0903_00862_001_07b.jpg%3F20170903091232&h=4488149b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都係入番室內合照穩陣啲。<br />\n<br />\n藝人阮兒、白雲、趙希洛與岑潔儀等日前一同出席餐廳開幕活動，場面熱鬧！阮兒自言喜歡吃英式菜色，例如炸魚薯條，故這家餐廳相當合她口味。提到活動當日發生了一段小插曲，阮兒指在危急下更「拯救」了白雲一命！<br />\n<br />\n阮兒笑說：「剪完綵影相時出咗少少意外，嗰度有三級樓梯，白雲睇唔到，跌落兩級，我救咗佢，但唔覺意推一推佢，唔覺意摸到佢個胸，好彩我係女仔。」而白雲則猶有餘悸表示：「好樣衰呀！我即刻擰轉面，因為好多人望住。」講到她跌落樓梯的一刻，她的35E導彈上圍差點「破衫而出」，她就笑言：「件衫唔係好性感，但佢（阮兒）推一推我，就好誇張咁。」阮兒亦為好友解畫：「因為剪完綵之後落雨，地下好跣，大家走避，白雲以為自己跑到，點知跣腳。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170903/bkn-20170903083626996-0903_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170903%2Fbkn-20170903083626996-0903_00862_001.html&d=HRfJxQQ%2BkWe4jdeiczQ95uargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=8fdb6726\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170903/bkn-20170903083626996-0903_00862_001.html</a>"}]}